        },
        "body": "This PR fixes two grammatical issues in the README to improve clarity and maintain proper parallel sentence structure.\r\n\r\n### 1. Added missing commas for a non-restrictive clause\r\n- \"Its low-level approach built on web standards...\"\r\n  → \"Its low-level approach, built on web standards, offers...\"\r\n\r\n### 2. Restored proper parallel verb structure in present perfect tense\r\n- \"has powered ..., become ..., and fostered ...\"\r\n  → \"has powered ..., has become ..., and has fostered ...\"\r\n\r\nThis maintains correct parallelism and preserves the intended meaning.\r\n\r\nNo functional or code changes — documentation only.\r\n",
